intentName: Alert Triage Ingestion to Array of Alert v1.0.2
description:
Retrieves incidents after a given time, extracts the first RFC822 attachment from those incidents.

Takes inputs
start_time: Incidents from that time will be pulled into turbine to get processed. 

Configuration:
Variables set in the "Create Custom Query" action, 
the End time and Include Ack must be defined.
name: Darktrace Get Incidents (VIC)
